  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with any congenital or acquired upper limb structural abnormalities

          -  Patients' condition is not suitable for surgical intervention or patients are not keen
             for surgical treatment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients have no available muscle signal input

          -  Patients fitted with a pacemaker or an implantable cardioverter defibrillator (ICD) or
             other implantable electrical devices

          -  Patients with contact dermatitis
      </textblock>
